                <li>✅ <span class="highlight">Admin Approval System</span>: Ensures quality and consistency of all materials.</li>
                <li>🤖 <span class="highlight">AI Chatbot (ChatGPT)</span>: Find papers, ask academic questions, and get suggestions via natural chat.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>🧠 Why Use Question Papers Hub?</h2>
